						"description": "Supabase JWT. Empty or absent for guest access."
					},
					"transport": {
						"type": ["string", "null"],
						"description": "Preferred transport: \"webtransport\" or \"websocket\".\nControls the order of server addresses in the ConnectToken so\nthe Netcode handshake tries the right port first. Defaults to\n\"webtransport\" for backward compatibility (Chrome prefers WT)."
					}
				}
			},
